{"tid":1301991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[失焦？] 我黎答你點解唔需要再set deadline","createTime":"2019-07-09T19:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T17:13:29.000Z","uid":154486,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8ac818b5f3af0e3eb63e350c0759c86b6843afbb","tid":1301991,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:47:11.000Z","msg":"有D on9懶醒就話大家已經失焦唔再提deadline<br />\n我黎同你講點解冇Deadline<br />\n<br />\n之前要set deadline係因為要出師有名，不能夠隨便就衝，否則民意會收皮<br />\n<br />\ndeadline &gt; 衝 &gt; 和平 &gt; deadline<br />\n呢個係加速段做既野<br />\n<br />\n而家大家既敵人已經由後面既林鄭轉到面前既差佬，而家民氣勁到baba聲<br />\n對住呢D黑社會撚樣就唔再需要同佢假仁假義，學梁天琦話齋：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地就係要耍無賴</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你話想要隻揪？我地成班人圍揪你又如何<br />\n你以為冇人還手自己好勁？下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家只有<br />\n和平-----------------&gt;<br />\n    衝    衝    衝    衝<br />\n<br />\n社運不能一本通書用到老<br />\n隨機應變先係致勝之道"},{"pid":"2bb56bb39a470ddfdbcf1aeb0b67b30c6441256d","tid":1301991,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:48:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d503739a6e6952162c7a07f18b1c2b6496542e6c","tid":1301991,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:49:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f456356088b7c1ea423b1df81f0b949b6703519e","tid":1301991,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:56:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f57ed8f125334e137ceccb3eeb93ef78235f57f0","tid":1301991,"uid":150809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a9e67bfed9d846ce1f6ee63aebf124a184f8cd","tid":1301991,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f57ed8f125334e137ceccb3eeb93ef78235f57f0","tid":1301991,"uid":150809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:56:57.